sisence is a BI tool like Tabluea

Download jar file from presto official site 

Place the jar file at location JDBC JARs Folder location below: 

use following connection config to connet to presto

Connection String
jdbc:presto://'public-ip-address':8889/hive/default   (default port used by presto is 8889)

JDBC JARs Folder
C:\Program Files\Sisense\DataConnectors\jdbcdrivers\presto

Driver's Class Name
com.facebook.presto.jdbc.PrestoDriver

